title: Blue Jays advance to American League Championship Series
text: Blue Jays advance to American League Championship Series Wednesday, 14 October 2015 (8 minutes ago) The Toronto Blue Jays advanced Wednesday to the American League baseball championship series with a wild 6-3 victory over the Texas Rangers. Rangers Outlast Blue Jays Over 14 Innings to Move Within One Win of ALCS 00:56 Backup infielder Hanser Alberto singled home the go-ahead run in the 14th inning and the Texas Rangers beat the Toronto Blue Jays 6-4 Friday for a 2-0 lead in the best-of-five American League Division Series.The underdog Rangers will try to sweep the Blue Jays at home in Game 3 Sunday.
